FT  16 SEP 92 / UK Company News: River &amp; Mercantile asset values ahead
River &amp; Mercantile American Capital and Income Trust had a net asset value
of 30.6p per capital share and 68p per income share at August 31 against
38.57p and 63.08p respectively a year earlier.
Net revenue for the half year amounted to Pounds 250,000 (Pounds 253,000)
for earnings of 3.33p (3.27p) a share. An unchanged second interim dividend
of 1.8p is declared, making 3.6p so far.
